Types ← [{"one" "two" "three"}
         {"solid" "open" "striped"}
         {"red" "green" "purple"}
         {"oval" "squiggle" "diamond"}]

Hand ← ˜↙⊏⍏⍥⚂⊸⧻≡≡⊡⊙(¤Types)⧅⋅⋅1 4⇡3 # build deck, shuffle, take N
Sets ← ≡(=1/↧≡(↥⊃=₁=₃⧻⊕⧻⊸⊛)⍉)       # each type in a set must be distinct or identical

Deal‼ ← (
  ⍢(^1◌|^0/+Sets(⧅<3))^1
  ⊸(▽⊸Sets(⧅<3))
)
&p"9 cards dealt, 4 sets available.\n"
≡&s⊙&sDeal‼(≠₄|Hand9)
&p"\n\n12 cards dealt, 6 sets available.\n"
≡&s⊙&sDeal‼(≠₆|Hand12)
